# PIA chat widget endpoint (n8n Chat Trigger webhook on the Plutus VPS).
# The widget falls back to this exact URL if the var is unset, so setting it is
# optional in production. Override it only to point the widget elsewhere
# (e.g. a localhost n8n during development, once that origin is allowed).
#
# CORS note: PIA's `allowedOrigins` only permits https://plutusintegrated.com,
# so the live chat round-trip succeeds only when the site is served from that
# domain (production). On a *.vercel.app preview URL the call will be blocked
# until that origin is temporarily added to allowedOrigins on the VPS.
NEXT_PUBLIC_PIA_CHAT_URL=https://automations.plutusintegrated.com/webhook/9a61995b-6eaf-46de-8071-ad5a5d60dc45/chat
